éation qu’ils ont mis en œuvre. C’est ainsi que chacun des chapitres de cet ouvrage permet de mieux comprendre les sous-textes des spectacles et des lectures présentés lors de la biennale 2015 et d’en saisir la portée artistique et sociale.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aCreation (Literary, artistic, etc.). 0aDrama festivalszOntariozOttawa. 0aExperimental theaterzCanadaxHistory and criticism. 0aFrench-Canadian dramay21st centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aReaders' theater. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aAllaire, Louise, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBeauchamp, Hélène, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChaîné, Francine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChaîné, Francine, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFrappier, Louise, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLansman, Émile, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeroux, Louis Patrick, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMelançon, Johanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNolette, Nicole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRuprecht, Alvina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aThéberge, Mariette, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aThéberge, Mariette, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTurbide, Yves, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVoyer-Léger, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017z9783111273